{"id": "1450843048732004362", "channel_id": "1450843048732004362", "type": 0, "author_id": "335454645251997717", "author_name": "iwthahe", "author_bot": false, "content": "Autoplay turning off after every stage is annoying and its strange that keeping it on isn't an option. I guess its only really usable when it comes to affinity farming, but still, wouldn't hurt, maybe someone out there likes autoplay.", "timestamp": "2025-12-17T13:32:18.178000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1450843048732004362", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」Would be nice for autoplay to remain turned on after finishing a stage.", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1450944805365616681", "channel_id": "1450944805365616681", "type": 0, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "If you kill the Boss but other mobs are out, you have to wait for them to explode to win, and is very strange.\nMaybe because i used Aigis Petrify on them before?\nThis is the Replay:\n Investigation-D-Effect Zone: Wave 3: Alert III Battle Replay\nKeeper: Leonora（100872341）\n\nHorla, Death of Ms. Coral, Poetic Bygone Days, Burial Ground's Sighs\nPollux, The Divus' Visage, Twisted Knight Ballad, April Tribute\nCastor, Unbearable Freedom, Lone Feather, Steppenwolf\nAigis, Winter's Requiem, Elevated Focus, Life Drain\nThe Lone Seed\n\n3b5992cf-9de1-3561-a994-c3e5d4e48221#E#a", "timestamp": "2025-12-17T20:16:38.850000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-17T20:17:03.833000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1450944805898162267", "filename": "fdrs.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 366011, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1450944805365616681/1450944805898162267/fdrs.JPG?ex=69cc2ba6&is=69cada26&hm=e30f88d2d9f328fba2c6bcb59aed8e0418465c4c3fd15ce545b0db0513e7945a&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1450944805365616681", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Another Bug? in Doll Boss", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
